file.name: issue11242.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Issue 11242 - Path Param encoding
  description: "White space encoding in path parameters"
  version: "1.0.0"
servers:
  - url: localhost:8080
paths:
  /api/{someParam}:
    parameters:
      - in: path
        name: someParam
        schema:
          type: string
        required: true
        description: Some parameter.
    get:
      operationId: GetSomeParam
      summary: View some param
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Some return value
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SomeReturnValue'
              example:
                someParam: someValue
components:
  schemas:
    SomeReturnValue:
      type: object
      required:
        - someParam
      properties:
        someParam:
          type: string
